Author: iwishiwereaballerina
Text: God, me too! It's driving me insane. I went into my holiday break thinking yay, I now have a great opportunity to restrict like crazy because I don't need energy to do my usual routine *but I'm not restricting and I don't know why*. In the past, I would've been happily restricting like crazy.   My mental state is just so oddly placid.
